social_posts.post_text: Don’t hit the wall. In fact, don’t destroy anything. PEOPLES! My new hour special “THE LAST LATE NIGHT” a talk show, stand up special is available on AMAZON PRIME, 12/2.

This is my wife, every time we go out to dinner. Shoot me. Peoples!!! My new hour special, “THE LAST LATE NIGHT” is avail on @amazonprime 112/2. A late night talk show, stand up special. Let’s do it!!!

AVAILABLE NOW!!! My new late night talk show, stand up special, THE LAST LATE NIGHT premiering on @primevideo 

A stand up special that takes place on the set of a late night talk show. Monologue jokes, panel/storytelling and traditional stand up. All with a band fronted by @nealsugarcaine and even commercial breaks. 

What I’m most proud of is this is paying homage to @officialjohnnycarson Plenty of Easter eggs in the special. But unlike EVERY SINGLE TALK AND POLITICAL SATIRE SHOW that just spews calculated vile at the right, I’m playing it right down the middle and joking with the left and right. @joebiden and @realdonaldtrump  Everyone gets it in this special. 

So, put this in your watchlist or tune in tonight! “The Last Late Night”, available on Amazon Prime. Best work I’ve ever done. Let me know what ya think… GODSPEED YA!
It’s official. “THE LAST LATE NIGHT” is now STREAMING on Amazon Prime. Free for Prime member. My late night talk show, stand up special. Unlike any other. Hope ya can check er out.

Peoples!!! Make sure to RATE/REVIEW “THE LAST LATE NIGHT” now streaming on Amazon Prime. The reviews and feedback has been the best I’ve ever had. THANKS AND LOVE to all for taking the time to watch!!!

The people have spoken! The response has been incredible, as it should!!! The new special, “THE LAST LATE NIGHT” is now streaming at Amazon Prime. A late night talk show, stand up special. Check it out! Rate! Review!!!

RATE/REVIEW, “The Last Late Night” now streaming on Amazon Prime. All this week, I’ll be posting the jokes that were banned from the release. Hope you enjoy them! And thanks to @pamela.sisson for capturing this moment in between tapings 1 and 2. LOVE & THANKS to all that have checked it out and passed along your thoughts! Means the world to me. This is by far, the most LOVE I’ve gotten from anything I’ve done in my career. And MUCH LOVE to my fellow comics and friends that have posted on their accounts to help spread the WORD. Appreciate ya. All of YAAAA!!! #TheLastLateNight

FATE? A SIGN? Coincidence? Before taping "The Last Late Night" my Amazon Prime special (now STREAMING), my pal/ director @joe_gatto placed a set of aces in the @officialjohnnycarson cigarette box on my desk. Little did he know, for the last 5 years, I've been carrying around an ACE in my wallet as a good luck charm that read "Hour 5" written on it. I couldn't believe it when I opened it. This was all caught in real time by @pamela.sisson on stage. Besides Joe coming in and crushing directing the special, he goes ahead and does this. He's the bestest!!! You’re always nervous before a taping but this made me feel like a million bucks.

Have you seen my new hour special "THE LAST LATE NIGHT" yet? It's rated 4.8//5 stars and streaming FREE at Amazon Prime and unlike any other comedy special out there. A late night talk show, hour special. It's the hardest I've worked on an hour, in fact, top to bottom, it took 5 years to put together. It would mean a lot if you could check 'er out and RATE/REVIEW BECAUSE it helps the algorithm. LINK in BIO. 

That being said, I wanted to THANK everyone who's been with me since I started stand up to those that just discovered me. It means the world I get to do this for a living and reading (the mostly) kind comments you all write each and every day, I wanted to say I APPRECIATE YOU!!! 

I hope to see you as I venture out on the road. Dates are all up at my website, stevebyrnelive.com. Again, THANK YOU for the laughs, the applause and the many hangovers.

2 years ago, a film I wrote and directed called “The Opening Act” was released. It’s a film about chasing your dream and ultimately what a 1st weekend on the road is like for a young comedian. Essentially, I took all the great road stories and wisdom I learned over 25 years in stand up and crammed it into 4 days in the movie. For a first time writer/director, the film sits at 83% FRESH. 

I not only got to work w my great pals Vince Vaughn and @officialpeterb but with some of the best comics working today and it all starts w the leads: @jimmyoyang @moffatpics and @cedtheentertainer Then along the way we have @wilfredburr @seguratom @whitneycummings @kenjeong @ilizas @russellpeters @roywoodjr @officialkathleenmadigan @joederosacomedy @nealbrennan @jermainefowler @debbyryan 

I’ll be posting clips and stories about the film all this week. I’m so proud of the work we accomplished on the film and even though it came out during pandemic and didn’t get the attention it deserved, I hope you can check it out. You can rent it at Amazon or ITunes for $2! Link: The Opening Act by Steve Byrne https://itunes.apple.com/us/movie/the-opening-act/id1533330775

A fun scene showcasing a typical bar show/open mic for any younger comics w @kenjeong @jimmyoyang @officialkathleenmadigan @breternst @petegiovine establishing how hard it is to get stage time when you get started. “The Opening Act” is avail to RENT/BUY wherever you get your movies. Happy Birthday to the film I got to write and direct. #TheOpeningAct

A scene where Will quits his job to pursue his dream. A fantastic scene with @jimmyoyang and @wilfredburr The shame of this scene is that Bill improv’d so many hilarious lines and unfortunately we had to cut them. We realized if we kept the jokes in the film, we’d lost the stakes of Will leaving his job and going all in on comedy. Emotionally, you want to feel like he’s losing and tip the scales to ramp up the stakes. If it’s funny, the stakes would’ve been lost and you don’t care if he wins or loses. Lessons learned in the edit room. Rent or buy “The Opening Act” 83% FRESH on Rotten Tomatoes #TheOpeningAct
